Package: skillviz
Title: Skill Co-Occurrence Analysis and Visualization from Online Job Advertisements
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti", , "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: Analyzes skill requirements from Online Job Advertising (OJA) data.
    Provides tools for computing skill specialization indices (Balassa/RCA),
    co-occurrence networks, source stability filtering, salary analysis,
    professional distance clustering, and temporal skill ranking. Built on
    ESCO and CP2021 (Italian professional classifications) taxonomies.
